items.checkin_comment: It’s like lucid dreaming, but hoppy. Pure Motueka magic with a cheeky splash of Riwaka, this one’s got you floating somewhere between sleep paralysis and euphoric citrus bliss. Smashing beer, just don’t forget to wake up for work tomorrow.
